List

9. Separate even and odd numbers into two different lists.

a = [1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6]
even = []
odd = []

for i in a:
    if i % 2 == 0:
        even.append(i)
    else:
        odd.append(i)

print("Even:", even)
print("Odd:", odd)

10. Find the second largest element in a list.

a = [10, 20, 40, 30, 50]
